Only change the file path to make it work, It will automatically create the files.
Tanha path'i file'aka bgora bo awai ish bkat, xoi fileakan drust akat.

public static  File fileUsers = new File("C:\\Users\\balen\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\Users.txt");
public static  File fileItems = new File("C:\\Users\\balen\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\Items.txt");
public static  File fileCheckoutHistory = new File("C:\\Users\\balen\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\CheckOutHistory.txt");
